A Midas-based DAQ software

-----------------------------------------
Requirements:
- a ROOT installation

-----------------------------------------
If it's already compiled, just set up 
your environment:
$ . setenv.sh
$ . thisdaq.sh

-----------------------------------------
Compilation:
- set environment variable ROOTSYS,
- compile midas:
  cd midas && make && cd -
- set MIDAS environment variables
- compile compress:
  cd compress && make && cd -
- compile crates:
  cd crateX && make && cd -

Or run the setup.sh script: ./setup.sh

